公式理解#2. 对 correlation modeling function  $\\mathcal{M}_1\\left(\\psi\\left(\\mathbf{x}_{\\mathbf{i}}\\right), \\phi\\left(\\mathbf{x}_{\\mathbf{j}}\\right)\\right)=\\sigma\\left(\\psi\\left(\\mathbf{x}_{\\mathbf{i}}\\right)-\\phi\\left(\\mathbf{x}_{\\mathbf{j}}\\right)\\right)$ 的理解#{1}":[74,80],"#Self Notes#公式理解#3. 对 Specifically, CTR-GC constructs a channel-graph for each channel with corresponding refined topology $\\mathbf{R}_{\\mathbf{c}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{N \\times N}$ and feature $\\tilde{\\mathbf{x}}_{:, \\mathbf{c}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{N \\times 1}$, where $\\mathbf{R}_{\\mathbf{c}}$ and $\\tilde{\\mathbf{x}}_{:, \\mathbf{c}}$ are respectively from $\\mathbf{c}$ -th channel of $\\mathbf{R}_{\\mathbf{c}}$ and $\\widetilde{\\mathbf{X}}\\left(c \\in\\left\\{1, \\cdots, C^{\\prime}\\right\\}\\right)$. 的理解":[81,89],"#Self Notes#公式理解#3. 对 Specifically, CTR-GC constructs a channel-graph for each channel with corresponding refined topology $\\mathbf{R}_{\\mathbf{c}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{N \\times N}$ and feature $\\tilde{\\mathbf{x}}_{:, \\mathbf{c}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{N \\times 1}$, where $\\mathbf{R}_{\\mathbf{c}}$ and $\\tilde{\\mathbf{x}}_{:, \\mathbf{c}}$ are respectively from $\\mathbf{c}$ -th channel of $\\mathbf{R}_{\\mathbf{c}}$ and $\\widetilde{\\mathbf{X}}\\left(c \\in\\left\\{1, \\cdots, C^{\\prime}\\right\\}\\right)$. 的理解#{1}":[82,89],"#Reading notes":[90,184],"#Reading notes#{1}":[91,95],"#Reading notes##💡 灵感":[96,101],"#Reading notes##💡 灵感#{1}":[98,101],"#Reading notes##😮 以前人们发现":[102,107],"#Reading notes##😮 以前人们发现#{1}":[104,107],"#Reading notes##🙈 其他论文的弊端或不足之处":[108,133],"#Reading notes##🙈 其他论文的弊端或不足之处#{1}":[110,133],"#Reading notes##😎 主要任务和重要发现":[134,162],"#Reading notes##😎 主要任务和重要发现#{1}":[136,162],"#Reading notes##📒 对模型的解释":[163,172],"#Reading notes##📒 对模型的解释#{1}":[165,172],"#Reading notes##⭐ 将来可能有用的地方；需要理解和记住的":[173,184],"#Reading notes##⭐ 将来可能有用的地方；需要理解和记住的#{1}":[175,184]},"outlinks":[{"title":"page. 1","target":"zotero://open-pdf/library/items/EV7X6HZ